dataType.content:
We may collect and process the following types of Personal Data in particular:
the information you provide by filling in forms on the Platform, in particular for the purposes of registering and personalising your account and participating in satisfaction surveys (e.g.: title, surname, first name, contact details, company, internal registration number etc.);
the information you provide for authentication, connection and internet browsing purposes (e.g.: identifiers, IP address, cookies etc.);
information you provide for the purpose of managing and paying for an order or service (e.g. dietary preferences, payment information etc.);
information you provide through posts, comments or other content you share with us.
Unless indicated as optional, the Personal Information to be provided is mandatory and if you do not provide this information, your request cannot be processed.
